      Video
      Founded in 2004, Facebook's mission is to give people the power to build community and bring the world closer together. People use Facebook to stay connected with friends and family, to discover what’s going on in the world, and to share and express what matters to them.

      Facebook is defined by our unique culture – one that rewards impact. We encourage people to be bold and solve the problems… · More they care most about. We work in small teams and move fast to develop new products, constantly iterating. Together, we can help people build stronger communities — we're just getting started.
